[[Asismel n Linné]] yessken-d amessdabu yettwasengel ar 7 n '''yidrasen igejdanen''' d 5 n '''yidrasen ussinen''' yettwaskan-d s ubellez amnursuy (ordre décroissant), s talɣa ayyi: 

: Imuddiren: '''[[Tagelda (tasnudert)|Tagelda]]''' → '''[[Astirf (tasnudert)|Adur]]''', '''[[Agzam (tasnudert)|Agzam]]''' → '''[[Asmil (tasnudert)|Asmil]]''' → '''[[Tafesna (tasnudert)|Tafesna]] '''→ '''[[tawacult (tasnudert)|Tawacult]]''' → [[Taɣreft (Tasartut)|Taɣreft]] → '''[[Tawsit (tudersent)|Tawsit]]''' → [[Tigezmi (tasnudert)|Tigezmi]] → [[Tamazrart (tasnudert)|Tamazrart]] → '''[[Talmest]]''' → [[Irzi]] → [[Talɣa (asismel)|Talɣa]]

'''idrasen imernayen''' am: «adu» , «afel», «azdar neɣ ader» gan d timerniwin a
ɣer isesmilen igejdanen amdya: [[adu-twacult]], [[Afelfesna]], [[Ader-adur]] ...

'''[[Talmest]]''' tesskanay-d adras agejdan n usismel [[Tasensartut (tasnudert)|asensarti]], w yal tikkelt mi ara ad tali tseddart n usesmel yettali neɣ yettnerni wemcabi gar igmamen (imɣan, iɣersiwen, iberčečča...).

